column7: [Business Wire] - IRVINE, Calif. & HONG KONG--(BUSINESSWIRE)-- Masimo (NASDAQ:MASI - News) announced Sunday at the World Congress of Anaesthesiologists (WCA) in Hong Kong that it has become the first Global Impact Partner of the World Federation of Societies of Anaesthesiologists (WFSA). The four-year partnership, “Safe Anaesthesia – ASAP” (Anesthesia Safety Action Plan), will initially identify one country with poor access to safe anesthesia, and will work toward implementing programs and training designed to improve anesthesia care and safe surgery outcomes. As part of the first phase of the joint project between the WFSA and Masimo, a high burden country will be identified as the ASAP’s focus.
